A malitela akwamozu Ụkọchukwu Oluwadamilare Temitayo Adeboye (Dare) bụ nwa nke atọ nke Ụkọchukwu Enoch Adeboye bụ onyeisi ụlọụka Redeemed Christian Church of God (RCCG).
A na-aka ụka maka akwamozu ya n'ụlọ ọgbakọ ndị ntoroọbịa dị na RCCG Redemption Camp dị n'Ogun steeti.
A kachaa ụka a, a ga-eli ozu ya taa bụ ụbọchị 11 nke ọnwa Mee, 2021.
